videos.description: Notre Dame guard Dane Goodwin fires up a 3-pointer and gets it to drop after several bounces on the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Notre Dame's Goodwin gets friendly bounce on 3-ball) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: Notre Dame's Goodwin gets friendly bounce on 3-ball

videos.description: Dane Goodwin gets hot from deep early, scoring nine straight points for Notre Dame with three consecutive 3-pointers.

videos.headline: Goodwin fired up after 3rd straight triple

videos.description: UCLA's Shareef O'Neal elevates to block TJ Gibbs' shot off the backboard, leading to Tyger Campbell's transition jumper.
